    "player_notes": "Dark hair, blue eyes. Female wolf named Ruhi. Older woman/protector - Magda - emissary of goddess of death. Following Dragonshits to Zorastor. Lord Santo was attacker of elven woman Emmerelda. Hanzo (dad). Baron Hesper - blue star - Mage/sorcerer - 'power behind the throne'. Constantine (Sylph's Embrace) and Marisette (Aphrodisias) - madames. Randall, Conall and Santo are all identical -- Hanzo is the father of all three. Brother taken by dragons as a child - dead or alive? Hanzo leads the Dragonshits. Brother's name? Gabriel. Conall: the warrior lady (Tamarack?) here to stop Hanzo. Santo is a fire-wielding magician, equal power to Conall. Soul blade -- used to bind a spirit in a body (possession), crafted by a necromancer. Girl who hugged me - Ila, 13.",
